[
  {
    "text": "The sun breaks the horizon at 614th.",
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Tanaka sees the Neanderthal army before she sees the light.",
    "start": 3.78,
    "end": 6.42
  },
  {
    "text": "They come in a wall, shoulder to shoulder.",
    "start": 6.94,
    "end": 9.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Room light glowing across 10,000 bodies like a single organism breathing blue fire.",
    "start": 9.8,
    "end": 14.22
  },
  {
    "text": "She gives the order.",
    "start": 14.88,
    "end": 15.76
  },
  {
    "text": "The disruptor activates with a sound no one hears.",
    "start": 16.46,
    "end": 18.66
  },
  {
    "text": "The air tastes of copper.",
    "start": 19.44,
    "end": 20.46
  },
  {
    "text": "The nearest Neanderthal's stumble, the room scars flicker.",
    "start": 21.26,
    "end": 24.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Their bone armor hardest titanium five seconds ago cracks along the seam lines.",
    "start": 24.7,
    "end": 28.54
  },
  {
    "text": "The first volley of incendiary rounds hits and this time the fire does not go out.",
    "start": 29.18,
    "end": 33.9
  },
  {
    "text": "The bone burns.",
    "start": 34.36,
    "end": 35.42
  },
  {
    "text": "The warriors fall.",
    "start": 36.14,
    "end": 36.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Tanaka counts.",
    "start": 37.78,
    "end": 38.5
  },
  {
    "text": "One human casualty for every four Neanderthals.",
    "start": 39.16,
    "end": 41.56
  },
  {
    "text": "The mat has changed.",
    "start": 42.12,
    "end": 43.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Her soldier's cheer.",
    "start": 43.88,
    "end": 44.64
  },
  {
    "text": "She does not.",
    "start": 45.18,
    "end": 46.0
  },
  {
    "text": "The disruptor will field extend 600 meters from the emitter.",
    "start": 46.66,
    "end": 49.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Beave on that range, the rooms glow at full power and the Neanderthals walk through",
    "start": 50.0,
    "end": 53.74
  },
  {
    "text": "gunfire like rain.",
    "start": 53.74,
    "end": 54.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Khaig's forces adapt within minutes.",
    "start": 55.46,
    "end": 57.16
  },
  {
    "text": "They spread their formation.",
    "start": 57.62,
    "end": 58.62
  },
  {
    "text": "They send flanking units around the fields perimeter.",
    "start": 59.2,
    "end": 60.96
  },
  {
    "text": "The line holds.",
    "start": 61.64,
    "end": 62.4
  },
  {
    "text": "But the line is a circle and the circle is getting smaller.",
    "start": 63.1,
    "end": 66.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Tanaka watches the flanks.",
    "start": 67.52,
    "end": 68.6
  },
  {
    "text": "She calculates.",
    "start": 69.08,
    "end": 69.88
  },
  {
    "text": "She needs more emitters.",
    "start": 70.5,
    "end": 71.56
  },
  {
    "text": "She needs more time.",
    "start": 71.86,
    "end": 72.74
  },
  {
    "text": "She has neither.",
    "start": 73.42,
    "end": 74.14
  }
]